OL,3,CGuernsey regulator says Sure's
OL,4,Cbroadband prices are "far too high"
OL,6,FGuernsey's competition regulator has
OL,7,Fsaid that Sure - who provide the
OL,8,Fisland's broadband - need to lower
OL,9,Ftheir prices by nearly a third.
OL,11,FGuernsey Competition and Regulatory
OL,12,FAuthority (GCRA) say the wholesale
OL,13,Fcost of broadband is "far too high"
OL,14,Fand puts "needless pressure on the
OL,15,Fcost of living for households by
OL,16,Fcharging excessive prices".
OL,18,FThe independent regulator has now
OL,19,Finstructed Sure to lower its prices
OL,20,Ffrom 1 April 2024 by 31%.
